hine creating new Internet-based trading markets in a wide range of commodi=
ties. ?But some of its new businesses faded, a large investment in an India=
n power plant went sour, the California power crises spooked investors, and=
 then Skilling stunned the financial community with his sudden resignation.=
 ?There also was grousing from investors that Enron's earnings statements h=
