Fantasy Football puts you at the helm of your own team of
NFL stars. The CBS SportsLine.com Fantasy Commissioner allows
Martin Cuilla to make all your league's rules and run 
your league in virtually any way possible. 

You'll enjoy the convenience of a private web site which 
stores all your team's data and updates the statistics and
